1. “Learn from other people’s mistakes, it’s much more convenient.”
2. People waste too much water in the shower.  Make it quick. 
3. Add frozen blueberries to hot oatmeal to cool it down.
4. Disney is a magical place where children’s dreams do come true.
5. Fresh orange juice, always.
6. You shouldn’t watch more than 2 episodes of tv in row.
7. When walking with a woman, a gentleman always walks on the side of the curb.
8. Reward good customer service, even if it means driving to the post office 2 towns away when there is one across the street.
9. Create a special way to tell the one you love that you love them, without words, that only you two know, and tell them often.